{"tid":572884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信微博無法修改頭像等個人資料","createTime":"2018-02-26T03:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T04:16:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ef648e9c55c5004c4927b765bfa9a6db8a9b3003","tid":572884,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/02/26/1775585_28843bf9eef3a1be119598005d27d2d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F1775585_28843bf9eef3a1be119598005d27d2d2.jpg&h=f19c7d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n騰訊、微博等平台昨晚發出公告，昨日起至3月底，用戶暫時無法修改頭像、暱稱及個性簽名等個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n微信稱，微信頭像、暱稱及個性簽名、QQ空間個人資料內容暫時無法修改，無法使用QQ群投票功能。<br />\n<br />\n微博方面，無法更改微博暱稱及頭像個人資料，無法修改公眾平台的功能介紹、頭像、暱稱。預計將於3月起恢復正常，其他功能不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1775585/微信微博無法修改頭像等個人資料\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1775585%2F%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E9%A0%AD%E5%83%8F%E7%AD%89%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%BA%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99&d=Z54oJ6CSA4JkzC1adIlY6ghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=3b06256a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/current/article/1775585/微信微博無法修改頭像等個人資料</a>"},{"pid":"444f788dd46c115e0101e1c4583df49344438387","tid":572884,"uid":12208,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"560bf17ce60b1560240a59f6d25add484ceaaa73","tid":572884,"uid":9564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g